    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors correctly scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 requirements for Class II devices at MRL 2. The hemolysis damage model methodology is further supported by the computational hemolysis benchmarking study referenced in the assessment literature (referencesIdentifier). Relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 confirmed for all worst-case operating points. Model credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
